Director
EIICHI YAMAMOTO

00:02:48.540 --> 00:02:58.540
Once upon a time...

00:03:00.540 --> 00:03:10.540
A kind young man and
a beautiful young woman

00:03:14.620 --> 00:03:21.539
Were joined in love

00:03:24.100 --> 00:03:34.100
Jean and Jeanne

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:43.419
Dancing in the sky of bliss

00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:53.619
Smiled upon by God

00:03:58.540 --> 00:04:06.379
Drunk on happiness

00:04:37.140 --> 00:04:41.619
Jean and Jeanne

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:47.419
Together forever

00:04:48.180 --> 00:04:52.539
Smiled upon by God

00:04:53.540 --> 00:04:56.939
Forever with each other..

00:05:00.620 --> 00:05:02.539
May they live happily ever after.

00:05:03.140 --> 00:05:05.819
But our story is just beginning.

00:05:08.020 --> 00:05:09.099
Your highness,

00:05:09.380 --> 00:05:14.379
today your loyal subjects
Jean and Jeanne

00:05:14.740 --> 00:05:21.179
were joined in holy matrimony.

00:05:24.180 --> 00:05:31.379
Honoring tradition, Jean has come to make

00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:37.019
an offering to show his gratitude.

00:05:56.460 --> 00:06:00.819
Your highness, please accept this money
in exchange for Jeanne's hand.

00:06:01.260 --> 00:06:04.579
We sold our milk cow to get it.

00:06:05.020 --> 00:06:08.539
How many milk cows?

00:06:09.300 --> 00:06:12.379
One. We have only one cow.

00:06:12.860 --> 00:06:14.379
Ten cows.

00:06:15.140 --> 00:06:19.579
Your highness is ordering
you to pay ten cows in tax!

00:06:20.780 --> 00:06:27.379
What?! I beg you...
We're too poor to pay ten cows.

00:06:27.820 --> 00:06:31.219
Your ladyship, have pity!

00:06:32.820 --> 00:06:36.059
Is this child chaste?

00:06:37.020 --> 00:06:45.059
I vow on my soul
that it was a pure marriage.

00:06:45.460 --> 00:06:50.339
Jeanne has never done anything unseemly.

00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:53.259
Earnest and hard working,

00:06:53.580 --> 00:06:56.139
the pride and joy of our village.

00:06:56.740 --> 00:07:00.379
Child, do you love this man?

00:07:00.700 --> 00:07:02.219
Yes, your ladyship!

00:07:02.660 --> 00:07:03.739
And you her?

00:07:04.140 --> 00:07:04.619
Yes!

00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:11.659
Listen everyone, after milord has had his
turn, you're all entitled to this offering!

00:09:34.820 --> 00:09:39.059
Let's forget what happened.
Our life starts from this moment.

00:10:38.020 --> 00:10:44.019
What is that flickering

00:10:46.100 --> 00:10:51.619
In the pale mirror?

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:57.059
Not tears,

00:10:58.140 --> 00:11:01.139
Not sighs,

00:11:01.860 --> 00:11:11.860
But tomorrow's vanished scraps.

00:11:17.660 --> 00:11:20.699
Or could it be...

00:11:21.660 --> 00:11:31.660
A woman's leaden body.

00:11:41.180 --> 00:11:47.579
What is that howling

00:11:49.420 --> 00:11:55.139
In the black sunset?

00:11:57.340 --> 00:12:00.379
Not the night wind,

00:12:01.460 --> 00:12:04.299
Not a crow,

00:12:05.460 --> 00:12:15.460
But a creaking hinge of rusted hope.

00:12:21.580 --> 00:12:23.819
Or could it be...

00:12:25.420 --> 00:12:35.420
A woman's painful moan.

00:13:00.740 --> 00:13:02.819
Don't worry.

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:08.099
Look how tired he is.

00:13:08.820 --> 00:13:10.379
Don't wake him.

00:13:11.940 --> 00:13:15.819
Who are you?
Where did you come from?

00:13:16.820 --> 00:13:18.459
You called me.

00:13:19.340 --> 00:13:20.459
I did?

00:13:21.140 --> 00:13:23.859
I'm sure I heard it...

00:13:24.620 --> 00:13:26.299
Your soul was screaming,

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:32.379
"I want power. Someone help me."

00:13:33.660 --> 00:13:35.379
And also...

00:13:36.300 --> 00:13:38.459
"I'll give anything...

00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:41.019
if someone would save me...

00:13:41.460 --> 00:13:44.019
even my soul."

00:13:44.300 --> 00:13:46.779
Are you the devil?

00:13:47.300 --> 00:13:49.299
I am you.

00:13:52.660 --> 00:13:55.699
That tickles. Stop it!

00:13:55.980 --> 00:14:00.019
I want to give you power.
As you wished.

00:14:00.820 --> 00:14:04.019
A tiny thing like you!

00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:08.419
It's your fault that I'm tiny.

00:14:09.300 --> 00:14:10.419
My fault?

00:14:11.020 --> 00:14:11.939
Yes.

00:14:13.020 --> 00:14:22.019
I can become as big
and as strong as you want me to.

00:14:22.540 --> 00:14:24.619
It's all up to you.

00:14:35.020 --> 00:14:36.779
You're so funny!

00:14:40.860 --> 00:14:43.139
You're laughing!

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:46.619
It's good to finally
see you happy.

00:14:46.940 --> 00:14:48.619
You're right.

00:14:49.900 --> 00:14:51.219
I...

00:14:52.100 --> 00:14:53.779
laughed.

00:14:55.140 --> 00:14:57.819
I thought I'd never laugh again.

00:14:58.300 --> 00:15:00.659
I understand you, Jeanne.

00:15:01.460 --> 00:15:04.299
I've always been by your side.

00:15:05.100 --> 00:15:07.939
I know everything about you.

00:15:08.820 --> 00:15:12.019
I told you, I am you.

00:15:13.140 --> 00:15:14.539
Stop that!

00:15:29.540 --> 00:15:30.979
What are you...?

00:15:32.380 --> 00:15:34.459
Where'd you go?

00:16:12.100 --> 00:16:15.219
You're doomed at this rate.

00:16:16.140 --> 00:16:21.739
Pray all you want...
Just look at your husband, Jean!

00:16:22.540 --> 00:16:25.139
Earnest and hard working,

00:16:25.420 --> 00:16:32.339
he should be in his prime,
but he's already breaking down.

00:16:33.300 --> 00:16:35.699
He'll probably get sick.

00:16:36.180 --> 00:16:38.459
Probably won't make it past the winter.

00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:40.619
Don't!

00:17:00.780 --> 00:17:05.059
I don't want anything,

00:17:06.660 --> 00:17:08.739
I don't need anything,

00:17:10.140 --> 00:17:11.619
I just...

00:17:12.100 --> 00:17:14.299
want to save him.

00:17:15.900 --> 00:17:17.419
Please...

00:17:18.260 --> 00:17:20.259
help me save him.

00:17:21.140 --> 00:17:23.939
Now that's more like it!

00:17:34.260 --> 00:17:37.579
Jeanne went to town to sell her thread.

00:17:42.020 --> 00:17:44.139
The town was starving again that year,

00:17:44.420 --> 00:17:48.459
but the lord still collected taxes.

00:17:49.660 --> 00:17:54.099
People were crushed by despair
and too weak to cry out.

00:17:56.660 --> 00:17:59.819
The only one working was Jeanne.

00:18:03.620 --> 00:18:05.379
The town.

00:18:13.100 --> 00:18:16.379
Jeanne's thread sold for a good price.

00:18:16.700 --> 00:18:19.379
No one even wanted to haggle.

00:18:22.020 --> 00:18:25.019
Jeanne's husband Jean was
the only one in the village

00:18:25.340 --> 00:18:27.379
able to pay the lord's high taxes.

00:18:27.700 --> 00:18:33.579
Rumors started spreading that
Jeanne was possessed by the devil.

00:18:37.020 --> 00:18:40.899
Delighted that Jean
had payed all his taxes,

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:45.019
the lord appointed
Jean town tax collector.

00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:50.259
Before only a poor peasant,

00:18:50.580 --> 00:18:53.579
now Jean was an official in a red hat.

00:18:53.860 --> 00:18:57.819
Jeanne was happy for
her husband's success.

00:18:58.820 --> 00:19:02.979
But Jeanne also noticed
that the villagers had changed.

00:19:03.300 --> 00:19:05.339
Now they bowed deeply,

00:19:05.660 --> 00:19:08.939
and avoided crossing paths
with Jean and Jeanne.

00:19:45.100 --> 00:19:55.100
The darkness is burning

00:20:05.060 --> 00:20:15.060
The darkness invites and seduces me

00:20:20.100 --> 00:20:27.019
Burning darkness

00:20:33.460 --> 00:20:39.019
Deep into it...

00:20:40.220 --> 00:20:47.019
Blazing hot...

00:20:50.140 --> 00:21:00.140
The darkness is burning...

00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:13.699
Get away!

00:21:29.700 --> 00:21:31.459
What do you want from me?

00:21:32.100 --> 00:21:37.019
This is only the beginning.

00:21:49.300 --> 00:21:53.379
Indeed, this was only the beginning
of Jeanne's suffering.

00:21:56.300 --> 00:21:58.219
War broke out.

00:21:58.780 --> 00:22:00.819
War is expensive.

00:22:01.300 --> 00:22:03.819
But winning meant more land.

00:22:05.100 --> 00:22:09.379
I'm leaving for the front tomorrow,
and this is all you collected?

00:22:10.020 --> 00:22:11.019
Yes...

00:22:11.620 --> 00:22:14.539
but tomorrow I promise...

00:22:14.820 --> 00:22:19.379
Fool! It takes more than
a few drops to turn a mill!

00:22:19.820 --> 00:22:23.619
If you don't get all the money in
three days, I'll have you hanged!

00:22:24.340 --> 00:22:28.219
But your highness... no one
has any more money left!

00:22:28.540 --> 00:22:32.419
Teach this man to listen to orders.

00:22:33.300 --> 00:22:36.059
Make his body remember.
Chop off his left hand.

00:24:07.380 --> 00:24:09.819
You called me?

00:24:11.220 --> 00:24:12.379
I did...

00:24:12.820 --> 00:24:14.739
I'll help you.

00:24:15.260 --> 00:24:18.619
I know you want power.

00:24:21.460 --> 00:24:23.259
You're cruel.

00:24:25.820 --> 00:24:30.019
You're mine now.

00:24:30.300 --> 00:24:33.259
Your body, your soul.

00:24:33.580 --> 00:24:35.019
Lies!

00:24:37.620 --> 00:24:41.379
My soul belongs to Jean

00:24:43.140 --> 00:24:47.979
and to God.

00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:54.219
You beautiful fool.

00:24:54.660 --> 00:25:01.739
Still you resist me,
even when you're beneath the rod!

00:25:04.940 --> 00:25:09.939
Your husband is on
the road to perdition.

00:25:10.460 --> 00:25:12.619
What will you do now?

00:25:17.900 --> 00:25:21.619
You're mine already,

00:25:23.140 --> 00:25:31.619
but I want you to accept me
of your own free will.

00:25:32.460 --> 00:25:37.819
I also want your heart and soul.

00:25:39.260 --> 00:25:42.219
Otherwise, he will...

00:25:45.820 --> 00:25:50.299
This flesh, this rotting flesh,

00:25:51.100 --> 00:25:54.619
I'll give it to you,

00:25:55.140 --> 00:25:58.739
if it will save Jean.

00:26:00.580 --> 00:26:03.379
But not my soul.

00:26:05.180 --> 00:26:09.339
I will never give you my soul!

00:26:16.660 --> 00:26:21.819
Very well then. Hang onto it
for a bit longer.

00:27:39.140 --> 00:27:41.219
What, Jeanne?

00:28:31.460 --> 00:28:33.339
Jeanne put on her green dress

00:28:33.660 --> 00:28:35.619
and went straight into town.

00:28:36.300 --> 00:28:38.219
They say green is the color of power,

00:28:38.540 --> 00:28:42.019
the color of the devil.

00:28:47.220 --> 00:28:50.819
The greedy old moneylender

00:28:51.100 --> 00:28:53.739
who had even refused
to lend money to the lord

00:28:54.020 --> 00:28:58.219
took one look at Jeanne
and loosened his purse strings.

00:28:59.140 --> 00:29:01.219
Later he grumbled,

00:29:02.100 --> 00:29:05.379
"That woman must be
possessed by the devil."

00:29:15.020 --> 00:29:18.179
Men love war in every age.

00:29:18.700 --> 00:29:24.379
The lord marched off in splendid array
with his soldiers and conscripted farmers.

00:29:26.220 --> 00:29:29.019
Women are always the
ones left behind to suffer.

00:29:41.940 --> 00:29:44.819
The men were gone for a long time.

00:29:46.820 --> 00:29:49.379
Several years passed.

00:29:54.860 --> 00:29:57.059
Jeanne had become a moneylender

00:29:57.380 --> 00:30:02.379
and gained control of the town.

00:30:04.900 --> 00:30:09.379
People feared and revered Jeanne
more than the lord's wife

00:30:09.820 --> 00:30:13.419
and obeyed her gladly.

00:30:29.420 --> 00:30:32.539
Who is in charge of this land while
his lordship is away?

00:30:33.420 --> 00:30:35.219
Me or that woman?

00:30:35.540 --> 00:30:37.259
You, of course!

00:30:37.580 --> 00:30:38.819
I didn't ask you.

00:30:39.100 --> 00:30:42.379
You're right to be angry, milady...

00:30:42.700 --> 00:30:47.019
But the war has been prolonged.
Without her help,

00:30:47.340 --> 00:30:49.259
even we wouldn't have enough to eat...

00:30:49.580 --> 00:30:50.619
Silence!

00:30:51.020 --> 00:30:54.019
That witch will pay for this.

00:30:56.460 --> 00:31:00.419
However, despite his newfound stature,

00:31:00.740 --> 00:31:03.619
Jean spent his days drinking.

00:31:13.740 --> 00:31:16.739
Suddenly, the lord
returned from the war.

00:31:23.140 --> 00:31:28.019
Women and men were overjoyed
to find each other again.

00:31:40.100 --> 00:31:43.379
The Lady rarely left her castle
to avoid seeing Jeanne,

00:31:43.820 --> 00:31:47.819
but that day she went to the church
on the plaza to greet her husband.

00:31:52.060 --> 00:31:55.819
Jeanne was there, too.

00:31:57.300 --> 00:32:00.339
I've never seen that woman before.

00:32:00.660 --> 00:32:06.019
Milord, things have been turned
upside down while you were away.

00:32:06.380 --> 00:32:07.739
What?

00:32:08.020 --> 00:32:10.739
That farmer bitch is in
league with the devil.

00:32:11.020 --> 00:32:13.379
The devil?

00:32:13.820 --> 00:32:17.979
The villagers respect her
more than anyone now.

00:32:18.380 --> 00:32:19.819
More than you, even.

00:32:20.140 --> 00:32:21.059
Is this true?

00:32:21.340 --> 00:32:22.539
Yes.

00:33:05.460 --> 00:33:08.019
Satanic fiend!

00:34:27.140 --> 00:34:33.579
Jean! Open the door! Hurry!

00:34:37.660 --> 00:34:39.099
Help!

00:34:40.140 --> 00:34:41.619
Jean!

00:34:42.580 --> 00:34:46.379
So you... didn't kill her.

00:34:47.020 --> 00:34:51.979
Even better.
We'll burn her alive at the stake!

00:34:52.460 --> 00:34:55.459
That's the best medicine for
witches in league with the devil.

00:34:55.780 --> 00:35:00.379
Heresy must indeed be
nipped in the bud.

00:35:00.860 --> 00:35:07.379
However, if we burn her body
while her soul belongs to Satan...

00:35:09.060 --> 00:35:10.859
What will happen?

00:35:11.140 --> 00:35:16.699
If we set her body aflame
on the mountain of tinder

00:35:17.140 --> 00:35:26.819
only for her soul to survive the flames
in its haughty pride,

00:35:28.580 --> 00:35:32.379
then, though her body had died,

00:35:32.820 --> 00:35:35.219
Satan would live on in her soul

00:35:35.540 --> 00:35:40.219
and might spread like sparks
from a fire to those all around.

00:35:40.900 --> 00:35:42.379
What do you suggest?

00:35:43.140 --> 00:35:48.339
Milady, you must lock her
deep in a dungeon

00:35:48.700 --> 00:35:51.419
and hold onto the keys.

00:35:52.300 --> 00:35:54.579
Then scourge her body

00:35:54.860 --> 00:35:57.619
until the light of God
shines into her soul

00:35:58.460 --> 00:36:03.019
and teaches her meekness.

00:36:04.260 --> 00:36:07.019
Very well. I'll see to it.

00:36:07.860 --> 00:36:10.299
Bring her to me!

00:37:01.860 --> 00:37:07.379
What is burning

00:37:10.300 --> 00:37:16.019
In the dark judgement?

00:37:17.660 --> 00:37:20.819
Not grief,

00:37:21.820 --> 00:37:24.939
Not penitence,

00:37:25.700 --> 00:37:35.700
But the silhouette of one exhausted.

00:37:41.340 --> 00:37:44.379
Or could it be...

00:37:45.660 --> 00:37:55.660
A woman's strong resentment.

00:38:05.420 --> 00:38:12.019
What awaits

00:38:13.300 --> 00:38:19.819
In the pale march of time?

00:38:21.100 --> 00:38:24.299
Not a life,

00:38:25.460 --> 00:38:28.539
Not a grave,

00:38:29.380 --> 00:38:39.380
But the mirage of a dead heart.

00:38:45.700 --> 00:38:48.619
Or could it be...

00:38:49.660 --> 00:38:59.660
A woman's crimson blood.

00:41:25.620 --> 00:41:27.939
So you've finally come,

00:41:28.300 --> 00:41:30.379
my beloved!

00:41:31.060 --> 00:41:35.139
Spit on by all, and now
abandoned by your own husband!

00:41:37.140 --> 00:41:41.019
How I've been waiting for this moment!

00:41:45.100 --> 00:41:49.259
Jeanne, since the day you were
born into this world,

00:41:49.780 --> 00:41:51.379
you were my friend,

00:41:51.700 --> 00:41:52.459
my ally.

00:41:52.780 --> 00:41:56.379
You and I have been
destined for one another,

00:41:57.300 --> 00:42:00.219
because of your wicked heart

00:42:00.700 --> 00:42:03.659
and devilish charm.

00:42:03.940 --> 00:42:07.219
It was you who pulled me down!

00:42:08.340 --> 00:42:11.739
Touching me... exciting me...

00:42:12.140 --> 00:42:13.019
into this hell!

00:42:13.300 --> 00:42:14.579
Exactly!

00:42:14.860 --> 00:42:18.019
A black dog bit me, that was you!

00:42:18.460 --> 00:42:20.019
His fangs cut me.

00:42:20.300 --> 00:42:22.379
Thorns tore into my flesh.

00:42:22.700 --> 00:42:24.139
Those were you too!

00:42:24.860 --> 00:42:26.219
They burned like fire.

00:42:26.540 --> 00:42:28.019
That's right!

00:42:28.740 --> 00:42:31.459
But I'm also the one who saved you.

00:42:32.220 --> 00:42:33.339
Saved me?

00:42:33.660 --> 00:42:39.219
I have no need for puny souls
who would throw themselves at my feet.

00:42:40.340 --> 00:42:42.259
My lust hungers for souls

00:42:42.580 --> 00:42:45.059
crushed under the weight of despair,

00:42:45.340 --> 00:42:51.739
driven to cursing God, mad for vengeance.

00:42:54.700 --> 00:42:57.179
Yours is coming along quite nicely!

00:43:05.900 --> 00:43:10.419
Ah, how beautiful you are today.

00:43:11.260 --> 00:43:17.019
The state of your body, your spirit...

00:43:17.580 --> 00:43:22.739
That is what stokes my desire
and fills me up!

00:43:28.460 --> 00:43:30.019
Satan!

00:43:30.700 --> 00:43:32.819
So they call me.

00:43:35.420 --> 00:43:40.139
Now, my wife.
Tell me what you want.

00:43:40.460 --> 00:43:42.619
I'll give you anything.

00:43:43.100 --> 00:43:45.019
What do you want to do?

00:43:58.820 --> 00:44:00.379
Something bad.

00:44:00.700 --> 00:44:01.819
What?

00:44:04.140 --> 00:44:08.019
Anything... so long as it's bad.

00:44:10.300 --> 00:44:14.019
Good answer! That's the Jeanne I know!

00:44:16.420 --> 00:44:21.619
Now give me your womb, Jeanne,
your soul...

00:44:22.660 --> 00:44:25.979
And take what I have to give!

00:47:36.820 --> 00:47:41.219
Spring came around,
even to the desolate wilderness.

00:47:42.740 --> 00:47:45.779
Suddenly Jeanne discovered
that she was not alone.

00:47:47.140 --> 00:47:50.619
Nature was there.

00:47:51.820 --> 00:47:57.939
You are beautiful, Jeanne.

00:47:59.700 --> 00:48:04.659
It can't be!
I thought I had gone to hell.

00:48:07.740 --> 00:48:09.219
This is hell?

00:48:12.300 --> 00:48:16.139
I gave myself to Satan.
I should be a wrinkly old witch by now.

00:48:16.620 --> 00:48:19.299
My hair a tangle of
venomous serpents,

00:48:19.820 --> 00:48:21.819
my skin green like a toad,

00:48:22.300 --> 00:48:25.219
black flames coursing
through my veins!

00:48:27.580 --> 00:48:32.979
This can't be me.
I'm being deceived!

00:48:34.780 --> 00:48:38.619
I want to become a horrifying woman.

00:48:39.260 --> 00:48:42.019
I want people to turn away in horror

00:48:42.420 --> 00:48:44.619
when I pass by in the street.

00:48:44.900 --> 00:48:46.899
I don't want to forget anger and hatred!

00:48:47.180 --> 00:48:52.299
Who says anger and hatred are ugly?

00:48:52.740 --> 00:48:55.939
You have become beautiful, Jeanne...

00:48:56.860 --> 00:48:58.219
Yes...

00:48:58.660 --> 00:49:01.619
Like a young girl in love...

00:49:02.620 --> 00:49:05.059
radiant.

00:49:05.900 --> 00:49:09.619
You are even more beautiful than God.

00:49:18.100 --> 00:49:22.379
Back in the village, it was
another bleak springtime.

00:49:26.820 --> 00:49:30.619
Jean was back to being
an ordinary farmer.

00:49:33.460 --> 00:49:35.819
Nothing had changed...

00:49:36.420 --> 00:49:39.619
until a dark shadow
crept upon the village.

00:49:42.820 --> 00:49:48.619
The black death.
Infection spelled certain death.

00:54:13.380 --> 00:54:15.619
Michel, you've noticed.

00:54:18.660 --> 00:54:20.099
Who are you?

00:54:20.700 --> 00:54:22.819
Jeanne, the witch.

00:54:23.740 --> 00:54:26.779
Wh... Where are we?

00:54:27.740 --> 00:54:29.859
Out of this world.

00:54:30.300 --> 00:54:32.019
It's all coming back to me now.

00:54:32.580 --> 00:54:38.619
I was taken for dead
and dumped in the graveyard.

00:54:39.140 --> 00:54:42.019
Last I remember
is trying to crawl out.

00:54:43.860 --> 00:54:46.379
I didn't expect to see you
in the afterworld.

00:54:47.660 --> 00:54:48.339
What are you doing?

00:54:48.660 --> 00:54:49.539
It's medicine.

00:54:49.900 --> 00:54:52.899
Liar! That flower's poison!

00:54:53.180 --> 00:54:57.619
Poison is medicine.
That is what cured you.

00:54:58.700 --> 00:55:00.339
Are you trying to kill me?

00:55:01.100 --> 00:55:03.619
I thought you were already dead?

00:55:24.340 --> 00:55:27.379
Michel's back from the dead!

00:55:28.180 --> 00:55:29.459
He's cured.

00:55:29.780 --> 00:55:31.019
How did it happen?

00:55:33.340 --> 00:55:38.379
Must be a witch!

00:55:41.660 --> 00:55:47.379
A witch... A witch...

00:56:13.220 --> 00:56:15.899
Famine and the plague
have devastated the village.

00:56:16.180 --> 00:56:19.259
The surviving villagers
must be starving.

00:56:19.580 --> 00:56:23.539
Yet they sing and dance all night

00:56:23.860 --> 00:56:26.379
at that witch's festivities
in the wilderness!

00:56:26.740 --> 00:56:29.099
Magic! Black magic!

00:56:29.380 --> 00:56:30.579
But it can't be.

00:56:31.060 --> 00:56:35.739
The villagers bring their
own food and drink.

00:56:36.100 --> 00:56:37.259
Filthy swines!

00:58:30.020 --> 00:58:33.299
That woman is still alive?

01:03:19.660 --> 01:03:25.699
It's a colorful flower.
She extracts juice from it.

01:03:26.180 --> 01:03:32.019
One sip and my wife's
labor pain went away.

01:03:32.780 --> 01:03:34.339
If I remember correctly...

01:03:34.660 --> 01:03:40.219
"Belladonna, a beautiful woman"

01:03:41.060 --> 01:03:43.139
that's what Jeanne called that flower.

01:03:45.340 --> 01:03:49.379
We just can't afford to have
any more children!

01:03:50.060 --> 01:03:50.939
But...

01:03:51.220 --> 01:03:53.739
My husband wants to every night...

01:03:54.380 --> 01:03:57.819
I feel bad to make him suffer.

01:03:58.460 --> 01:04:01.779
And I get lonely too.

01:04:02.380 --> 01:04:11.459
So we asked Jeanne if there was a way
to do it without making children.

01:04:12.300 --> 01:04:17.019
Oh we know it's bad and wrong
in God's eyes.

01:04:17.700 --> 01:04:19.699
It's an awful sin.

01:04:20.700 --> 01:04:25.699
But no punishment could be
worse than what we've suffered.

01:04:28.260 --> 01:04:31.339
Now we're happy.

01:04:32.260 --> 01:04:36.059
We don't regret it,
no matter the punishment.

01:04:37.180 --> 01:04:43.819
I wanted to see my grandson,
who died on the battlefield.

01:04:44.140 --> 01:04:50.379
I heard Jeanne could
bring back the dead.

01:04:52.260 --> 01:05:00.019
Jeanne cried her eyes out
when she heard my story.

01:05:01.060 --> 01:05:05.379
She gave me a stick of tobacco

01:05:06.300 --> 01:05:10.939
and some blood-red wine to drink.

01:05:12.100 --> 01:05:13.179
Well?

01:05:13.900 --> 01:05:16.019
Did your dead grandson come back?

01:05:16.540 --> 01:05:18.019
No.

01:05:18.620 --> 01:05:20.659
Did you at least hear his voice?

01:05:21.100 --> 01:05:22.339
No.

01:05:22.660 --> 01:05:25.539
Then you were deceived!

01:05:26.060 --> 01:05:28.619
I got on my knees crying

01:05:29.100 --> 01:05:32.379
and began to pray.

01:05:33.380 --> 01:05:36.819
My body was burning up.

01:05:37.660 --> 01:05:41.539
It all seemed like a dream.

01:05:42.660 --> 01:05:47.979
I built up my courage
and raised my eyes...

01:05:49.380 --> 01:05:51.059
What did you see?

01:05:51.540 --> 01:05:59.979
I could see the host of hellfire

01:06:00.540 --> 01:06:03.819
wailing for my grandson!

01:06:08.740 --> 01:06:12.219
You mean to say that satisfied you?

01:06:12.540 --> 01:06:14.379
Oh yes!

01:06:15.300 --> 01:06:20.659
I've never been so happy.

01:06:26.620 --> 01:06:31.219
Lord save us all.
It's a rebellion against God.

01:06:32.020 --> 01:06:34.379
A revolt against you, milord!

01:06:34.820 --> 01:06:36.859
Seize that woman at once!

01:06:37.220 --> 01:06:38.219
Burn her at the stake!

01:06:38.540 --> 01:06:44.739
But the road is rough
and the villagers are on her side.

01:06:45.100 --> 01:06:47.579
She will run before
our soldiers get there.

01:06:47.860 --> 01:06:50.939
Who is lord of this land? You? Or...

01:06:51.220 --> 01:06:55.939
Be patient. We must wait for the
enemy to reveal her weakness.

01:06:56.700 --> 01:06:58.459
Leave it to me!

01:08:12.180 --> 01:08:14.299
What ails you, little one?

01:08:15.460 --> 01:08:17.379
Do you want me?

01:08:19.700 --> 01:08:20.659
Jeanne...

01:08:22.100 --> 01:08:23.779
Don't you recognize me?

01:08:24.900 --> 01:08:29.019
I'm the Lady's page.

01:08:29.540 --> 01:08:32.659
She hates you, so I hated you too.

01:08:33.380 --> 01:08:37.299
I'm the one who
slashed your green cloak.

01:08:37.620 --> 01:08:39.179
Your point, little page?

01:08:39.460 --> 01:08:41.219
I did it because...

01:08:41.580 --> 01:08:45.019
I love her.

01:08:45.540 --> 01:08:46.939
Are you here to kill me?

01:08:47.220 --> 01:08:48.779
I need your help, Jeanne.

01:08:49.460 --> 01:08:51.379
Hear my plea.

01:08:51.940 --> 01:08:55.139
I want to make love to her.

01:08:55.460 --> 01:08:56.379
But...

01:08:56.780 --> 01:09:01.539
I'm only a lowly page.
She'd never consider me.

01:09:01.820 --> 01:09:03.379
Who cares about status?

01:09:03.940 --> 01:09:08.019
God granted us our status.

01:09:09.100 --> 01:09:12.699
Ignoring that is against God!

01:09:13.300 --> 01:09:14.819
The work of the devil!

01:09:15.260 --> 01:09:16.539
However...

01:09:17.140 --> 01:09:20.179
I'm willing to sell myself
to the devil for my love.

01:09:20.460 --> 01:09:22.139
Enough.

01:09:23.420 --> 01:09:25.299
Filthy witch!
How dare you!

01:09:37.180 --> 01:09:38.379
Very well,

01:09:40.340 --> 01:09:41.819
I'll help you.

01:12:45.460 --> 01:12:47.819
Crafty wench...

01:12:50.180 --> 01:12:53.819
She succeeded where
the black death failed

01:12:54.100 --> 01:12:58.019
in penetrating the sanctum
of the castle.

01:12:58.300 --> 01:13:01.019
Lord, we must act at once!

01:13:01.300 --> 01:13:03.019
Call that man!

01:13:28.020 --> 01:13:29.339
It's you...

01:13:32.820 --> 01:13:34.099
It's been a long time.

01:13:35.180 --> 01:13:36.219
Yeah.

01:13:52.620 --> 01:13:54.699
You don't look happy, Jean.

01:13:58.340 --> 01:14:00.379
Is it too late for us?

01:14:02.820 --> 01:14:10.219
Stop this madness and come live
a normal life with me on the farm again.

01:14:13.100 --> 01:14:16.979
Please forgive me for what I did.
I had no choice.

01:14:17.260 --> 01:14:19.019
Don't...

01:14:21.100 --> 01:14:22.579
I've forgotten about all that.

01:14:25.060 --> 01:14:26.619
Come back with me

01:14:27.420 --> 01:14:28.179
to the castle.

01:14:28.460 --> 01:14:29.779
The castle?

01:14:30.260 --> 01:14:33.139
His lordship has said
he'll forgive your crimes.

01:14:33.580 --> 01:14:36.379
Not only that,
he acknowledges your skills!

01:14:37.020 --> 01:14:41.819
You helped the people
get over their suffering.

01:14:42.260 --> 01:14:43.779
He was in awe of your goodness!

01:14:46.380 --> 01:14:48.619
And you believe him, Jean.

01:14:49.620 --> 01:14:52.699
His lordship says he wants
to join forces with you.

01:14:53.620 --> 01:14:57.379
What good is your knowledge about
healing herbs and soothing wine,

01:14:57.860 --> 01:15:03.179
without the power of the king
so it can reach all the land?

01:15:05.940 --> 01:15:09.699
His lordship could have sent his troops
to capture you or kill you.

01:15:10.260 --> 01:15:12.379
But he doesn't want that!

01:15:13.020 --> 01:15:15.539
If you give him all your knowledge,

01:15:15.900 --> 01:15:19.139
he promised we could live
quietly on a parcel of land.

01:15:19.420 --> 01:15:22.059
And if I refuse?

01:15:22.740 --> 01:15:25.139
You'll be killed, Jeanne!

01:15:26.100 --> 01:15:28.219
You... and me both!

01:15:31.100 --> 01:15:34.059
Jeanne, please do as I say!

01:17:41.300 --> 01:17:44.739
Don't think of this as a trade, Jeanne.

01:17:45.380 --> 01:17:50.059
Think of it as a pact
between you and I,

01:17:50.420 --> 01:17:53.619
to find a path to lead
the people to happiness!

01:17:54.420 --> 01:18:00.979
The fertile plot of 100 acres is but
a humble sign of my goodwill.

01:18:02.300 --> 01:18:08.019
Now please tell the scientists
how to use that strange flower.

01:18:11.100 --> 01:18:15.419
What's the matter?
100 acres not enough?

01:18:18.460 --> 01:18:19.939
Well then,

01:18:20.340 --> 01:18:22.979
how does the village chief sound?

01:18:24.260 --> 01:18:28.379
We'll even make you nobility!
How about it?

01:18:29.740 --> 01:18:31.819
Jeanne, what are you...

01:18:32.180 --> 01:18:39.539
Fine!
Head of nobility, second only to me!

01:18:40.060 --> 01:18:40.859
What do you say?

01:18:41.700 --> 01:18:42.659
No.

01:18:44.100 --> 01:18:46.379
I don't need any of that.

01:18:48.100 --> 01:18:51.579
Wh... What on earth do you want, then?

01:18:52.380 --> 01:18:53.619
Everything.

01:18:55.220 --> 01:18:56.459
What?

01:18:57.820 --> 01:18:59.419
The entire world!

01:19:01.220 --> 01:19:02.939
All of it.

01:19:14.780 --> 01:19:16.139
Prepare the stake!

01:19:16.620 --> 01:19:21.379
I want this witch burned
at the stake this instant!

01:24:52.020 --> 01:24:53.379
Jean...

01:25:55.780 --> 01:25:59.379
Time passed.

01:26:08.900 --> 01:26:14.699
On July 14, 1789 at the Bastille.
At the head of the French Revolution stood...

01:26:19.100 --> 01:26:23.539
The women.

01:27:00.900 --> 01:27:03.619
